title: WikiLeaks CableGate - second update for February 2nd, 2011 - 12:
description:
WikiLeaks.ch CableGate update for February 2nd, 2011 (12:21 PM).  This is a second update for this date - the first was at 12:42 AM.


The cablegate-201102021221.7z is 8.11 MB in size (8,506,162 bytes), and expands to 265 MB (277,987,654 bytes), containing 4,741 files in 136 folders.

If you're seeding an older CableGate torrent, seed this instead.  The Pirate Bay and sites that pull torrents from it can be a few hours / days behind, but you can always get the latest torrent on the bottom of http://wikileaks.ch/cablegate.html

If you run a local WikiLeaks "pull" / "scrape" mirror (search P2P networks for "wikileaks scrape"), then extract this update in the Web path.  These 7z files can be extracted with WinRAR or 7zip for Windows, or p7zip for any operating system.

The bad guys can put up blocks to all known / major HTTP mirrors at any time, which is why grabbing, seeding, and otherwise proliferating the latest torrents is very important!
